Web & Script Assignment 3 - Project Plan

Project: HobbyHub

Description: An online platform where users can discover, share and explore hobby ideas. Each hobby listing provides information such as average cost, solo or group activity, required materials and category (arts, sports, tech, etc.). 

Purpose: Help people find new hobbies that fit their lifestyle, budget and interests. Users can add their own suggestions about things they are passionate about or read about others hobbies when they are bored and need something new. 

Features: 
  * User friendly home page introducing the site and how it works
  * CRUD (create, read, update, delete) for functionality for managing hobby listings 
  * Responsive design by Bootstrap
  * MangoDB for storing hobby data

Page descriptions:
1. Home page:
    - First page user sees, introduces HobbyHub and explains the purpose of the application
2. All hobbies page:
    - Displays all hobbies stored in the database (READ)
    - Allows you to edit or delete hobbies
3. Add hobbies page: 
    - Allows users to create a new hobby to the website (CREATE)
        - Form fields: 
            * Hobby name
            * Description
            * Average cost
            * Solo/Group type
            * Materials 
        - Buttons: 
          * Save hobby
          * Cancel 
4. Edit and Delete hobby page:
    - Allows user to modify an existing hobby (UPDATE)
    - Allows users to remove a hobby from the database (DELETE) 

